message.content: cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.SY. This paper discusses the concept of action in robotics and proposes a taxonomy for categorizing action representations. The paper is likely to be classified under cs.RO (Robotics) as it primarily focuses on the role of action in robotics research. However, it also involves concepts related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), and systems and control (cs.SY) which are relevant to the study of action representations in robotics.
